{"tid":2322281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"驗屍報告證俄仇女KOL女友非凍死 死因係頭部重創! KOL承認曾「重毆頭部」佢老母泣訴：我仔好乖架","createTime":"2020-12-12T08:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T12:10:48.000Z","uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb9e0338551a4e4e90883e89579e15d6f953d02","tid":2322281,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:03:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201212/ZGYVPH7KIRDD5IA3YARQYHB24I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201212%2FZGYVPH7KIRDD5IA3YARQYHB24I%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jckx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=5d742776\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201212%2FZGYVPH7KIRDD5IA3YARQYHB24I%2F&h=76a0192e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201212/ZGYVPH7KIRDD5IA3YARQYHB24I/</a><br />\n俄羅斯一名化名為「Reeflay」的30歲直播主雷舍特尼科夫(Stas Reshetnikov)，在本月2日為了「斗內」、有粉絲支付1000美元(約新台幣2.8萬元)，竟然把懷孕女友在幾近全裸的狀態下，把她丟在屋外，讓她活活凍死。<strong><span class=\"red\">但最後驗屍報告出爐，28歲女友格里戈里耶娃(Valentina Grigoryeva)的真正死因並非凍死，而是頭部遭到重創，雷舍特尼科夫也終於向警方承認，女友在死前曾對她暴力毆打。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n不過雷舍特尼科夫的母親葉林娜(Elena)日前接受媒體訪問時，不斷強調：「我兒子很乖的！」葉林娜表示，雷舍特尼科夫在求學時期就是一名乖學生，也曾進入軍隊服役，他不相信自己的兒子是惡人。葉林娜也說，雷舍特尼科夫做直播主，其實收入不高，但她不相信雷舍特尼科夫會為了錢，去做出傷天害理之事。不過對於格里戈里耶娃的死，葉林娜也表示她相當難過，並請求女方家屬的原諒。"},{"pid":"6f1e69243a7ac5eff3f215d439165a3ed5848600","tid":2322281,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d1ac36bdce6af62bd0a77d6e6aabea41461502","tid":2322281,"uid":284432,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2aff7f58e77c6b6eff8c827074a3b680f145574",